use celery to receive book information from internet
requires:
   celery == 2.5.3
   django-celery == 2.5.5
   odfpy

suggest 
using pip install them

1.start celery
	python manage.py celeryd
2.start django
	python manage.py runserver

USAGE:
1. first add book reader in http://site/admin/
   to ad a book reader
2. choose book reader in EDIT

